cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

The paper deals with a machine learning problem of predicting multiple target variables from a common set of input variables. This is a common problem in several subfields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper proposes new methods for solving this problem and evaluates them on a diverse collection of datasets, which is a characteristic of machine learning research. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
